## How To Run The Demo
```powershell
powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\start_emotion_system.ps1
```
*(The script will automatically detect node/python, spawn the background API, start the React server, and cleanly shut them down automatically with `Ctrl+C`)*.
